[
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 3.682,
        "duration": 1.914
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a real\npleasure to welcome",
        "start": 5.596,
        "duration": 4.281
    },
    {
        "text": "Kris Bowers,\nour composer, who",
        "start": 9.877,
        "duration": 2.671
    },
    {
        "text": "has written a concerto,\n“For a Younger Self.”",
        "start": 12.548,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "Welcome.",
        "start": 16.229,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 16.729,
        "duration": 3.815
    },
    {
        "text": "Can I ask a question?",
        "start": 20.544,
        "duration": 1.876
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, Granddaddy.",
        "start": 22.42,
        "duration": 1.281
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you tell me, just\nwhat is a concerto?",
        "start": 26.256,
        "duration": 3.576
    },
    {
        "text": "So it's basically\nthis piece that",
        "start": 29.832,
        "duration": 2.821
    },
    {
        "text": "has a soloist and an\nensemble, an orchestra.",
        "start": 32.653,
        "duration": 4.021
    },
    {
        "text": "The two are having\na conversation.",
        "start": 36.674,
        "duration": 1.434
    },
    {
        "text": "And so sometimes\nthat conversation",
        "start": 38.108,
        "duration": 1.417
    },
    {
        "text": "can be this person speaking,\nand now this person speaking.",
        "start": 39.525,
        "duration": 3.188
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes the conversation —",
        "start": 42.713,
        "duration": 1.208
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a question.",
        "start": 43.921,
        "duration": 0.375
    },
    {
        "text": "— is at the same time.",
        "start": 44.296,
        "duration": 1.031
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 45.327,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "And it really depends on\nhow the composer wants to,",
        "start": 45.827,
        "duration": 3.801
    },
    {
        "text": "or how I want to frame\nthat conversation.",
        "start": 49.628,
        "duration": 3.896
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you ever picture yourself\ndoing what you're doing now?",
        "start": 53.524,
        "duration": 3.381
    },
    {
        "text": "Huh.",
        "start": 56.905,
        "duration": 2.112
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 59.017,
        "duration": 3.494
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 62.511,
        "duration": 4.592
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm very aware of the fact\nthat I'm a Black composer,",
        "start": 67.103,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "and lately actually I've\nbeen wondering whether or not",
        "start": 69.653,
        "duration": 2.356
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm supposed to be in\nthe spaces that I'm in,",
        "start": 72.009,
        "duration": 1.876
    },
    {
        "text": "or supposed to have\ngotten to the point",
        "start": 73.885,
        "duration": 1.625
    },
    {
        "text": "that I've gotten to.",
        "start": 75.51,
        "duration": 1.615
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, I can tell\nyou one thing.",
        "start": 77.125,
        "duration": 2.491
    },
    {
        "text": "Never think that you're\nnot supposed to be there.",
        "start": 79.616,
        "duration": 2.111
    },
    {
        "text": "Cause you wouldn't\nbe there if you",
        "start": 81.727,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "wasn't supposed to be there.",
        "start": 83.047,
        "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
        "text": "It goes back to slavery.",
        "start": 87.778,
        "duration": 5.588
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 93.366,
        "duration": 3.459
    },
    {
        "text": "My grandfather, who I found\nout has cancer a little",
        "start": 107.774,
        "duration": 3.551
    },
    {
        "text": "while ago, I wanted to spend\nsome more time with him",
        "start": 111.325,
        "duration": 5.161
    },
    {
        "text": "and talk to him about his\nlife, about our family,",
        "start": 116.486,
        "duration": 3.751
    },
    {
        "text": "ask him as much as I\ncan before he passes.",
        "start": 120.237,
        "duration": 3.231
    },
    {
        "text": "[BELL RINGING]",
        "start": 126.625,
        "duration": 2.406
    },
    {
        "text": "Granddaddy.",
        "start": 132.991,
        "duration": 0.705
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm-hm?",
        "start": 133.696,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Need a bit of\nhelp with this.",
        "start": 134.196,
        "duration": 2.636
    },
    {
        "text": "Do what?",
        "start": 136.832,
        "duration": 0.665
    },
    {
        "text": "Getting this seamed\nout for the show.",
        "start": 137.497,
        "duration": 2.781
    },
    {
        "text": "OK. Don't step\non the pedals.",
        "start": 140.278,
        "duration": 1.555
    },
    {
        "text": "Push it right in the corner.",
        "start": 145.294,
        "duration": 2.333
    },
    {
        "text": "OK. Wow.",
        "start": 147.627,
        "duration": 0.508
    },
    {
        "text": "OK.",
        "start": 148.135,
        "duration": 0.768
    },
    {
        "text": "We're going to make\nit real handsome here.",
        "start": 148.903,
        "duration": 1.793
    },
    {
        "text": "You're going to\nbe ready to go.",
        "start": 150.696,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you, sir.",
        "start": 152.636,
        "duration": 0.709
    },
    {
        "text": "Growing up in the South\nwas quite a thing for me.",
        "start": 157.768,
        "duration": 7.352
    },
    {
        "text": "Bascom, Florida, as far\nback as I can remember,",
        "start": 165.12,
        "duration": 4.571
    },
    {
        "text": "I think the plantation was\nthe Bowers plantation.",
        "start": 169.691,
        "duration": 3.651
    },
    {
        "text": "All 13 of you all\ngrew up in that house?",
        "start": 173.342,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm-hm.",
        "start": 175.732,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow.",
        "start": 176.232,
        "duration": 0.866
    },
    {
        "text": "How all of us stayed in\ntwo rooms, I don't know.",
        "start": 177.098,
        "duration": 4.416
    },
    {
        "text": "We would start on\nthe porch singing.",
        "start": 181.514,
        "duration": 3.491
    },
    {
        "text": "And there were\npeople, I don't know",
        "start": 185.005,
        "duration": 1.601
    },
    {
        "text": "how they could hear it\nthat far, would come drive",
        "start": 186.606,
        "duration": 2.601
    },
    {
        "text": "in the front yard and\nlisten to us sing at night.",
        "start": 189.207,
        "duration": 4.871
    },
    {
        "text": "People in that area was,\nthe Blacks were Bowers,",
        "start": 194.078,
        "duration": 5.091
    },
    {
        "text": "and the whites was Beavers.",
        "start": 199.169,
        "duration": 2.591
    },
    {
        "text": "Beavers had the grocery store.",
        "start": 201.76,
        "duration": 3.051
    },
    {
        "text": "But when Dad would\nwalk in the store,",
        "start": 204.811,
        "duration": 2.531
    },
    {
        "text": "this kid about my\nsize, small kid —",
        "start": 207.342,
        "duration": 2.772
    },
    {
        "text": "How old were you\nabout this point?",
        "start": 210.114,
        "duration": 1.459
    },
    {
        "text": "Like how old?",
        "start": 211.573,
        "duration": 0.701
    },
    {
        "text": "I probably was 6\nor 7 years old.",
        "start": 212.274,
        "duration": 3.309
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, wow.",
        "start": 215.583,
        "duration": 1.745
    },
    {
        "text": "And he would go up to my\ndad and say, what could I",
        "start": 217.328,
        "duration": 2.307
    },
    {
        "text": "get for you, boy?",
        "start": 219.635,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "That stuck with me forever.",
        "start": 221.285,
        "duration": 3.391
    },
    {
        "text": "Why are you calling\nmy dad a boy?",
        "start": 224.676,
        "duration": 3.031
    },
    {
        "text": "And Daddy would answer\nhim, sir, yes sir, no sir.",
        "start": 227.707,
        "duration": 6.105
    },
    {
        "text": "But it was something\nthat stayed with me",
        "start": 233.812,
        "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
        "text": "because I knew then\nwhen I got of age I",
        "start": 235.479,
        "duration": 3.559
    },
    {
        "text": "was going to leave there.",
        "start": 239.038,
        "duration": 1.043
    },
    {
        "text": "I didn't want no\nparts of the farm.",
        "start": 242.913,
        "duration": 1.459
    },
    {
        "text": "I didn't want no parts of\nthat part of the country.",
        "start": 244.372,
        "duration": 3.241
    },
    {
        "text": "I just wanted to leave.",
        "start": 247.613,
        "duration": 1.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Wherever I could\nget a ride to,",
        "start": 252.484,
        "duration": 3.251
    },
    {
        "text": "that's where I was headed to.",
        "start": 255.735,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 257.015,
        "duration": 10.633
    },
    {
        "text": "What was that process like,\nhitchhiking as a Black man",
        "start": 267.648,
        "duration": 3.295
    },
    {
        "text": "in America in the 1940s?",
        "start": 270.943,
        "duration": 1.717
    },
    {
        "text": "I had to be crazy.",
        "start": 272.66,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, the first place I\nremember being is in Detroit.",
        "start": 278.301,
        "duration": 5.872
    },
    {
        "text": "A man picked me up.",
        "start": 284.173,
        "duration": 1.29
    },
    {
        "text": "He was saying that he could\nget me a job and a place",
        "start": 285.463,
        "duration": 2.671
    },
    {
        "text": "to stay and all this.",
        "start": 288.134,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "I asked him, does\nit snow there?",
        "start": 289.254,
        "duration": 1.334
    },
    {
        "text": "And he said yes.",
        "start": 290.588,
        "duration": 1.322
    },
    {
        "text": "And that was the end\nof that, because I",
        "start": 291.91,
        "duration": 1.626
    },
    {
        "text": "didn't want to be any\nplace that was cold.",
        "start": 293.536,
        "duration": 3.521
    },
    {
        "text": "But I hitchhiked from\nthere to Denver, Colorado.",
        "start": 297.057,
        "duration": 4.641
    },
    {
        "text": "And I was in this\nGreyhound bus station,",
        "start": 301.698,
        "duration": 2.501
    },
    {
        "text": "cause they had two\ncounters, white and Black.",
        "start": 304.199,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "So I could get\nsomething to eat.",
        "start": 306.919,
        "duration": 2.341
    },
    {
        "text": "And I heard somebody say,\nLos Angeles, California.",
        "start": 309.26,
        "duration": 3.361
    },
    {
        "text": "I said, that's\nwhere I want to go.",
        "start": 312.621,
        "duration": 3.151
    },
    {
        "text": "Never heard of Los\nAngeles before.",
        "start": 315.772,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "I had $27 or $28.",
        "start": 318.492,
        "duration": 3.113
    },
    {
        "text": "I didn't know how I\nwas going to make it,",
        "start": 321.605,
        "duration": 1.709
    },
    {
        "text": "but I knew I was\ngoing to make it.",
        "start": 323.314,
        "duration": 2.03
    },
    {
        "text": "So I said well, I'm\ngoing to pretend",
        "start": 325.344,
        "duration": 3.511
    },
    {
        "text": "to be an employment agency\nand call around to get a job.",
        "start": 328.855,
        "duration": 5.772
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow.",
        "start": 334.627,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "I got the telephone\nbook, started at the A's.",
        "start": 335.127,
        "duration": 4.001
    },
    {
        "text": "A Cleaners.",
        "start": 339.128,
        "duration": 2.051
    },
    {
        "text": "And I don't think I made\nmore than five calls,",
        "start": 341.179,
        "duration": 3.681
    },
    {
        "text": "and the phone rang, and\nit was the A Cleaners,",
        "start": 344.86,
        "duration": 3.421
    },
    {
        "text": "and they said they\nneeded a presser.",
        "start": 348.281,
        "duration": 3.391
    },
    {
        "text": "I got all the information.",
        "start": 351.672,
        "duration": 1.39
    },
    {
        "text": "I said, OK, I'll\nsend someone right out.",
        "start": 353.062,
        "duration": 2.661
    },
    {
        "text": "And that was me.",
        "start": 355.723,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "[LAUGHING]",
        "start": 356.683,
        "duration": 4.891
    },
    {
        "text": "That's where I met\nyour grandmother.",
        "start": 361.574,
        "duration": 1.839
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 373.376,
        "duration": 8.614
    },
    {
        "text": "How old were you when\nyou bought the cleaners?",
        "start": 381.99,
        "duration": 3.491
    },
    {
        "text": "I was 20.",
        "start": 385.481,
        "duration": 1.841
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow.",
        "start": 387.322,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "So within two years I\nhad gone from homeless",
        "start": 387.822,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "to I was in business.",
        "start": 390.402,
        "duration": 3.661
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 394.063,
        "duration": 5.012
    },
    {
        "text": "But I never could get a loan.",
        "start": 399.075,
        "duration": 2.09
    },
    {
        "text": "And I owned the place.",
        "start": 401.165,
        "duration": 1.506
    },
    {
        "text": "I said, something wrong\nwith this picture.",
        "start": 402.671,
        "duration": 2.866
    },
    {
        "text": "I told them I come\nin for the loan,",
        "start": 405.537,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "and he said no, I\ndon't have anything.",
        "start": 408.117,
        "duration": 2.641
    },
    {
        "text": "And I left later, and\npicked up an application,",
        "start": 410.758,
        "duration": 4.991
    },
    {
        "text": "and I mailed it in.",
        "start": 415.749,
        "duration": 1.394
    },
    {
        "text": "A few days later, I got a\ncall, your loan is approved.",
        "start": 417.143,
        "duration": 5.098
    },
    {
        "text": "I said, it's the\ncolor of my skin.",
        "start": 422.241,
        "duration": 3.661
    },
    {
        "text": "I said in the South\nthey tell you.",
        "start": 425.902,
        "duration": 3.651
    },
    {
        "text": "In Los Angeles they show you.",
        "start": 429.553,
        "duration": 3.571
    },
    {
        "text": "From then on we started\nbuying property,",
        "start": 433.124,
        "duration": 3.071
    },
    {
        "text": "I would get things at\nthe cleaner, everything,",
        "start": 436.195,
        "duration": 2.691
    },
    {
        "text": "but nobody ever saw me.",
        "start": 438.886,
        "duration": 2.861
    },
    {
        "text": "Everything was done by mail.",
        "start": 441.747,
        "duration": 2.393
    },
    {
        "text": "People are constantly throwing up\nthings to stop you in life.",
        "start": 446.418,
        "duration": 3.531
    },
    {
        "text": "But you've got to know\nyou cannot stop me.",
        "start": 449.949,
        "duration": 6.432
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 456.381,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "My name is\nKristopher Bowers,",
        "start": 460.581,
        "duration": 3.205
    },
    {
        "text": "and I want to play “Shining\nStar in Atlantic City.”",
        "start": 463.786,
        "duration": 5.008
    },
    {
        "text": "My parents decided\nbefore I was born",
        "start": 468.794,
        "duration": 2.441
    },
    {
        "text": "they wanted me to play piano.",
        "start": 471.235,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Literally, I think it's called\nlike \"Piano Sampler No. 5\"",
        "start": 473.115,
        "duration": 2.611
    },
    {
        "text": "that they used to put on\nmy mom's stomach every day.",
        "start": 475.726,
        "duration": 6.362
    },
    {
        "text": "Actually, one of the first\npieces of music I ever wrote",
        "start": 482.088,
        "duration": 2.941
    },
    {
        "text": "was on this piano.",
        "start": 485.029,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "And I remember,\nyou know, just",
        "start": 486.099,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "playing around\nhere all the time.",
        "start": 487.669,
        "duration": 2.151
    },
    {
        "text": "But we were up at\na restaurant one,",
        "start": 489.82,
        "duration": 2.701
    },
    {
        "text": "I believe it was a Sunday.",
        "start": 492.521,
        "duration": 1.705
    },
    {
        "text": "At Marie Callendar's?",
        "start": 494.226,
        "duration": 1.021
    },
    {
        "text": "Marie Callendar's.",
        "start": 495.247,
        "duration": 1.765
    },
    {
        "text": "They had a piano in\nthere, and I asked",
        "start": 497.012,
        "duration": 2.311
    },
    {
        "text": "the guy could you play it.",
        "start": 499.323,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "And they said yes.",
        "start": 501.563,
        "duration": 1.211
    },
    {
        "text": "I carried you over there,\nand you were playing it,",
        "start": 502.774,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "and I was proud of you.",
        "start": 505.814,
        "duration": 2.141
    },
    {
        "text": "[LAUGHING]",
        "start": 507.955,
        "duration": 1.949
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 509.904,
        "duration": 4.468
    },
    {
        "text": "There aren't that\nmany opportunities",
        "start": 514.372,
        "duration": 1.965
    },
    {
        "text": "for young kids of color\nto showcase their talents",
        "start": 516.337,
        "duration": 5.962
    },
    {
        "text": "or to interact with\nother kids of color",
        "start": 522.299,
        "duration": 1.681
    },
    {
        "text": "playing music and\ndoing those things,",
        "start": 523.98,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "and you talking about\nbeing my manager,",
        "start": 526.02,
        "duration": 2.111
    },
    {
        "text": "essentially, from\nthe very beginning.",
        "start": 528.131,
        "duration": 3.692
    },
    {
        "text": "If I didn't have\nthat, I probably",
        "start": 535.053,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "wouldn't have been as\nconfident pursuing music.",
        "start": 536.883,
        "duration": 4.636
    },
    {
        "text": "I remember — where\nwere you in school",
        "start": 541.519,
        "duration": 2.206
    },
    {
        "text": "at that I was up there?",
        "start": 543.725,
        "duration": 1.515
    },
    {
        "text": "What, in New York?",
        "start": 545.24,
        "duration": 1.146
    },
    {
        "text": "At Juilliard?",
        "start": 546.386,
        "duration": 0.865
    },
    {
        "text": "Juilliard?",
        "start": 547.251,
        "duration": 1.055
    },
    {
        "text": "Wherever it was,\nyou enjoyed it.",
        "start": 548.306,
        "duration": 2.271
    },
    {
        "text": "So that's all I was thinking.",
        "start": 550.577,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "If you enjoyed making\na living at it.",
        "start": 552.457,
        "duration": 2.791
    },
    {
        "text": "I never thought that…far",
        "start": 555.248,
        "duration": 3.376
    },
    {
        "text": "And the winner\nis Kris Bowers.",
        "start": 558.624,
        "duration": 1.686
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Green Book.\"",
        "start": 565.948,
        "duration": 0.929
    },
    {
        "text": "[APPLAUSE]",
        "start": 566.877,
        "duration": 28.972
    },
    {
        "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
        "start": 595.849,
